  "detailed_description": "Manage your country and achieve your mission : conquer/protect a territory, destroy a country...<br><br>First, make bids to choose your territories.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714760/extras/6ee7bd794bb8bf81379633c3810fb683.avif?t=1753016318\" width=620 height=348 /></span><br><br>This part of the game requires already a good strategy :<br><br>How much is it worth to buy the territories you want ?<br><br><br><br>Then, enter the second part of the game. The action and strategy parts.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714760/extras/dcf4621f97578e67f6a3c3c1b5c1f2bf.avif?t=1753016318\" width=620 height=348 /></span><br><br>You can :<br><br>create alliances, or partnerships, of boycot, or ... declare war.<br><br>You can manage your resources :<br><br>- Craft wood<br><br>- Fish<br><br>- Mine gold , iron, uranium, oil<br><br>Make military craft :<br><br>- Tanks<br><br>- Helicopters<br><br>-Nuclear submarines",
